太晚了
It's late.

334
00:17:17,910 --> 00:17:18,940
我没那么饿
I'm not that hungry.

335
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:20,860
我们就去海军基地吧
Let's just get to the Navy Yard.

336
00:17:22,100 --> 00:17:24,000
我实在不想晚上去那里
I really don't want to spend the night there.

337
00:17:24,120 --> 00:17:25,780
希望这不会太长时间
Well,hopefully,it won't be for long.

338
00:17:25,850 --> 00:17:28,170
我们走楼梯吧 这样快点
Let's take the stairs.It's quicker.

339
00:17:30,410 --> 00:17:32,110
女士先请
After you.

340
00:17:37,970 --> 00:17:39,140
对不起
Sorry.

341
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:40,450
开门
Open it.

342
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,660
再见噢
Buh - bye.

343
