Brett!
Brett!

344
00:17:58,060 --> 00:17:59,940
协查通告有消息吗?
Any response to the BOLO?

345
00:18:00,070 --> 00:18:03,340
没有 我觉着一整天他都在晃点我
No. I felt,all day,he wanted to shake me.

346
00:18:03,530 --> 00:18:05,580
要保护不想被保护的人很难
It's hard to prect someone who doesn't want protection.

347
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,950
他手机仍然关机
His cell's still off.

348
00:18:07,040 --> 00:18:08,030
他今天早上的行程是什么?
What was his schedule this morning?

349
00:18:08,140 --> 00:18:12,400
他应该上午11:00到办公室 和珍珠港的Mosley海军司令开电话会议
Has to be in his office by 11:00 a.m. for a conference call with Admiral Mosley in Pearl Harbor.

350
00:18:12,490 --> 00:18:14,910
我怀疑他不会去了 Kaplan有线索吗?
I doubt he'll miss that.You got anything on Kaplan?

351
00:18:15,020 --> 00:18:21,540
没有人的特区驾照和护照地址是 Branchport大道1313号 西北边
There's no DC driver's license or passport issued to a George Kaplan at 1313 Branchport Avenue,Northwest.

352
00:18:21,600 --> 00:18:24,020
本想在全州范围内搜索 但那名字很大众化
We're trying surrounding states,but it's common name.

353
00:18:24,120 --> 00:18:25,030
肯定会有很多重名的
There's gonna be a lot of hits.

354
00:18:25,170 --> 00:18:27,210
- 服役或者犯罪记录? - 没有
- Military or criminal record? - None.

355
00:18:28,090 --> 00:18:30,130
有发现
I got something.

356
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:34,250
George Kaplan的社保号 登记在Branchport大道
The Social Security number of the George Kaplan on Branchport Avenue.

357
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:36,740
为什么这名字这么耳熟?
Why does that name sound so familiar?

358
00:18:36,850 --> 00:18:38,960
- 你从哪儿找到的社保号? - Kaplan的股票经纪人
- Where'd you get the number? - Kaplan's stockbroker.

359
00:18:39,010 --> 00:18:42,980
付完买凶的钱 他帐户里还有110万
Turns out he's got $1.1 mil in the account that paid for the hit man.

360
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:44,000
股票经纪告诉你的?
Broker give you a description?

361
00:18:44,080 --> 00:18:45,560
他从未见过他吧
Doesn't think he ever met him.

362
00:18:45,610 --> 00:18:48,520
与一个叫Drew Turner 的业务经理打交道
Dealt with the business manager,a Drew Turner.

363
00:18:48,830 --> 00:18:50,660
这和房东大娘说的名字一样
It's the same name we got from the landlady.

364
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:53,870
经纪人说是有点不寻常 总是和业务经理打交道
The broker says it's not unusual.Deals with business managers all the time.

365
00:18:53,930 --> 00:18:59,240
查到Turner有授权委托书- 他有开立帐户的所有文件
Turns out that Turner had power of attorney-- all the documentation you need to open an account.

366
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:02,630
这就是说他能拿到Kaplan 的社保号和地址
Which means he's got Kaplan's Social Security number and address,

367
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:05,430
那就是一个住处 不可能是邮政信箱
which has to be a residence; can't be a P.O. box.

368
00:19:04,100 --> 00:19:05,790
