{\a6}***

369
00:19:05,560 --> 00:19:08,240
Kaplan有存档州和联邦的捐税收入
Kaplan files state and federal tax returns.

370
00:19:08,340 --> 00:19:10,590
- 做帐的人是... - Drew Turner
- prepared by... - ...Drew Turner.

371
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:11,780
该去和他谈谈了
Time to talk to him.

372
00:19:11,850 --> 00:19:15,380
DiNozzo去拿Kaplan帐户记录的传票 马上
DiNozzo,subpoena the records of Kaplan's account... now.

373
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:25,730
Drew Turner?
Drew Turner?

374
00:19:25,820 --> 00:19:27,610
- 我是 - 你是个女的
- Yes. - You're a woman.

375
00:19:27,930 --> 00:19:29,890
那又怎样?
What gave it away?

376
00:19:30,030 --> 00:19:32,510
NCIS McGee和Dinozzo探员
NCIS. Agents McGee and DiNozzo.

377
00:19:32,610 --> 00:19:33,810
我们要跟你谈谈
We need to speak with you.

378
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:34,890
海军调查员
Navy investigators.

379
00:19:35,050 --> 00:19:39,700
我在国税局有个会面 快迟到了 所以...
I am running really late to a meeting with the IRS,so...

380
00:19:41,130 --> 00:19:42,620
请进吧
Come on in.

381
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:49,550
Drew Turner
Drew Turner.

382
00:19:49,650 --> 00:19:51,250
对 我今早才回到城里
Yeah,I just got back into town this morning.

383
00:19:51,320 --> 00:19:56,660
听着 他们只是在审计你的娱乐花费 我这就把你的发票都拿过去
Listen,they are only auditing your entertainment expenses and I'm bringing copies of all your receipts.

384
00:19:56,710 --> 00:19:59,590
放轻松 你没犯任何错 Harry
So relax,you have nothing to worry about,Harry.

385
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:05,100
对 我 呃 最多15分钟后到你那里
Yeah,I,uh,can meet you in ten... 15 minutes at the most.

386
00:20:05,350 --> 00:20:07,240
好的 再见
Okay,bye.

387
00:20:08,850 --> 00:20:11,100
紧张的客户 第一次被审计 不好意思
Nervous client.First time being audited.Sorry.

388
00:20:11,190 --> 00:20:14,500
在家办公...一定很不错
Must be nice... working out of your home.

389
00:20:14,820 --> 00:20:16,090
工作不挑时间
Never late to work.

390
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:18,260
是的 没错
Yeah,I bet.

391
00:20:18,340 --> 00:20:21,160
注册会计师 所以你也做个人纳税申报?
CPA.So you do personal tax returns?

392
00:20:21,340 --> 00:20:24,790
对 很不错嘛
Yeah. It's impressive.

393
00:20:24,860 --> 00:20:27,530
我们在找你的一个客户 George Kaplan
We're looking for a client of yours,George Kaplan.

394
00:20:27,610 --> 00:20:28,620
你知道哪里能找到他吗?
Do you know where we can find him?

395
00:20:28,690 --> 00:20:30,280
呃 你们去过他的公寓没?
Uh,you check his apartment?

396
00:20:30,380 --> 00:20:34,620
去过了 呃 也许他出城了 他好像经常到处跑
Yes. Okay,uh... maybe he's out of town.He seems to move around a lot.

397
00:20:34,670 --> 00:20:37,070
自从上次税季我就没见过他了
I haven't seen him since last tax season.

398
00:20:37,450 --> 00:20:39,340
- 你能描述一下他的外貌吗? - George?
- Can you describe him? - George?

399
00:20:39,410 --> 00:20:42,600
呃 不高 174左右
Yeah,um,on the shorter side,five-eight maybe.

400
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:44,070
黑发
Dark hair.

401
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:45,670
我真的不太了解他
I don't really know him that well.

402
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:48,950
我是说 我只是帮他处理投资帐户 一年做一次报税
I mean,I just helped him set up an investment account and do his taxes once a year.

403
00:20:49,830 --> 00:20:51,010
这到底是怎么回事?
What is this about?

404
00:20:51,110 --> 00:20:52,840
你认识一个海军少校叫 Geoffrey Brett的吗?
Do you know a Lieutenant Commander named Geoffrey Brett?

405
00:20:54,450 --> 00:20:56,500
不认识 对不起
No. Sorry.

406
00:20:56,580 --> 00:20:58,020
我得走了
And I gotta get going.

407
00:20:58,080 --> 00:21:01,710
我的客户正在国税局办公室里 这会让他过度呼吸而昏阙的
I mean,my client is at at the IRS office and he is hyperventilating.

408
00:21:02,450 --> 00:21:06,570
我们需要你来海军基地一趟 给Kaplan画个素描
Well,we just need you to come by the Navy Yard and help us with a sketch of Kaplan.

409
00:21:06,770 --> 00:21:07,950
你也在那儿吗?
Are you gonna be there?

410
00:21:08,050 --> 00:21:09,520
当然
Definitely.

411
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:15,730
你会跟我们的法证科学家 Abby Sciuto一起合作
You'll be working with our forensic scientist Abby Sciuto.

412
00:21:15,800 --> 00:21:16,580
都行
Whatever.

413
00:21:16,680 --> 00:21:20,130
一结束国税局的事情我就过去 大概一个 或者最多两个小时?
I mean,I'll be there as soon as I'm done with the IRS; let's say an hour,two at the most?

414
00:21:20,220 --> 00:21:22,510
那不错 谢谢
Sounds good.Thanks.

415
00:21:33,130 --> 00:21:34,140
我到底有多大麻烦?
How much trouble am I in?

416
00:21:34,210 --> 00:21:36,060
你不把对你生命的威胁当回事
You're not taking the threat on your life seriously.

417
00:21:36,110 --> 00:21:37,910
没错 我是不当一回事 完全是乌龙嘛
You're right,I'm not.It's bogus.

418
00:21:37,990 --> 00:21:40,320
你是一个专业杀手的目标
a professional hit man is targeting you.

419
00:21:40,410 --> 00:21:41,670
你无凭无据
You have no basis.

420
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:44,330
我没法想象 我身边有谁恨我恨成这样
I can't,for the life of me,think of anyone I've pissed off that bad.

421
00:21:44,410 --> 00:21:46,130
你为什么甩了我
Why'd you ditch me?

422
00:21:46,260 --> 00:21:48,460
好吧 这太古怪了
Okay,this is awkward.

423
00:21:48,580 --> 00:21:50,200
- 要听真话? - 那敢情好
- The truth? - That would be nice.

424
00:21:50,230 --> 00:21:52,800
整天开会你都跟着我 我觉得很不舒服
I was uncomfortable having you with me in meetings all day,

425
00:21:52,880 --> 00:21:56,150
但是昨晚决不能让你还跟着我
but there was no way I could let you accompany me last night.

426
00:21:56,270 --> 00:21:57,990
- 我跟一个女人在一起 - 已婚的?
- I was with a woman. - She married?

427
00:21:58,050 --> 00:22:01,070
不 她没有嫉妒心强的前男友 相信我 我想过这个
No,and no jealous ex-boyfriends.Trust me,I thought of that.

428
00:22:01,330 --> 00:22:03,820
你们俩根本不懂 我自己也有生活的
You two don't get it.I've got a life to live.

429
00:22:03,880 --> 00:22:07,870
如果有人要杀我 我能自己处理好
And if anyone's trying to kill me,I can take care of myself.

430
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:13,490
我真高兴这不是我的活
I'm glad this is your detail and not mine.

431
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:15,430
继续
Go on.

432
00:22:19,490 --> 00:22:22,070
- 有什么发现 Abbs - 哦 Gibbs 你吓了我一跳
- What do you got,Abbs? - Whoa,Gibbs,you scared me.

433
00:22:22,910 --> 00:22:23,790
你在做什么?
What are you doing?

434
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:28,570
呃 我在查路易斯安那州Jefferson Parish 所有的男性出生记录
Um,I'm searching male birth records from Jefferson Parish,Louisiana.

435
00:22:28,660 --> 00:22:29,930
找到啥了?
You find anything?

436
00:22:29,990 --> 00:22:31,010
没有
No.

437
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:33,790
Kaplan公寓里的指纹有发现吗?
How'd you make out with the prints found in Kaplan's apartment?

438
00:22:33,890 --> 00:22:36,130
呃 我还没处理
Um,I haven't gotten to them yet.

439
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,680
那Kaplan的素描呢?
What about the computer sketch of Kaplan?

440
00:22:37,780 --> 00:22:39,330
他的业务经理没来
His business manager never showed up.

441
00:22:39,390 --> 00:22:41,390
你告诉Tony和McGee了吗?
Did you tell Tony,McGee?

442
00:22:41,490 --> 00:22:45,670
- 没有 我无法集中精力 Gibbs - Abbs
- No. I've been a little distracted,Gibbs. - Abbs.

443
00:22:46,950 --> 00:22:48,530
我需要你
I need you.

444
00:22:52,960 --> 00:22:54,570
非常感谢
I appreciate it.

445
00:22:56,040 --> 00:22:59,320
经纪人说他收到Drew Turner的电话 那个火辣性感的会计师
Broker said he got a call from Drew Turner,the hot,sexy accountant,

446
00:22:59,380 --> 00:23:04,050
是上礼拜的事 授权把Kaplan帐户的钱 转往哥斯达黎加
last week,authorizing the money transfer to Costa Rica from Kaplan's account.

447
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:07,080
她告诉我们她自从上个税季就没有 跟Kaplan联系过
She told us she hadn't spoken to Kaplan since last tax season.

448
00:23:07,190 --> 00:23:08,010
她在撒谎
She lied.

449
00:23:08,090 --> 00:23:10,030
哦 我猜你不会请她帮你报税的
Well,I guess she won't be doing your taxes.

450
00:23:10,170 --> 00:23:11,260
我打给Gibbs
I'm going to call Gibbs.

451
00:23:11,350 --> 00:23:12,480
等一下 菜鸟
Hold it,probie.

452
00:23:12,590 --> 00:23:14,460
是我拿到经纪人资料的传票的
I'm the one who subpoenaed the brokerage papers.

453
00:23:14,580 --> 00:23:18,260
对 但是是我追踪钱转到赌博网站的
Uh,yeah,but I'm the one that traced the transfer to the gambling Web site.

454
00:23:28,740 --> 00:23:30,820
- 老大 是我 - 不 是我
- Boss,that's me. - No,actually,that was me.

455
00:23:30,890 --> 00:23:32,560
我拿到Kaplan的经纪状况了
I got Kaplan's brokerage statement.

456
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:38,490
在两万五美刀转入杀手的帐户一个礼拜以前 有一笔50万的取款
Week before the 25 grand was wired to the hit man,there was a $500,000 withdrawal.

457
00:23:38,570 --> 00:23:41,220
我追踪这笔钱 发现被汇入了哥斯达黎加 的一个赌博网站
I tracked it to an online gambling Web site in Costa Rica.

458
00:23:41,340 --> 00:23:45,120
转账人是Kaplan的业务经理 Drew Turner
Transaction was initiated by Kaplan's business manager,Drew Turner.

459
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:47,420
我们告诉过你Drew是个女的 是吧?
We told you that Drew is a woman,right?

460
00:23:47,510 --> 00:23:48,750
那是当然
Of course we did.

461
00:23:48,820 --> 00:23:52,570
她有权限进入这个帐户 这你也知道
She is authorized to sign on the account.You knew that,too.

462
00:23:52,660 --> 00:23:54,720
她告诉我们她有几个月 没有跟Kaplan联系了
She told us she hadn't talked to Kaplan in months.

463
00:23:54,810 --> 00:23:57,100
我们认为小坏猫正在做什么坏事
We think that little kitty cat is up to something.

464
00:23:57,210 --> 00:23:59,960
很显然 她跟George Kaplan是一伙的
Clearly,she and George Kaplan were in this together.

465
00:24:00,050 --> 00:24:02,800
Turner没有来跟Abby画素描
Turner did not show to do the sketch with Abby.

466
00:24:02,940 --> 00:24:04,440
把她带来
Bring her in.

467
00:24:17,480 --> 00:24:18,850
她不在家
She's not home.

468
00:24:18,970 --> 00:24:21,010
车子在这儿
Car's here.

469
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:24,500
我让Abby追踪她的手机
I'm going to have Abby track her cell.

470
00:24:31,540 --> 00:24:33,660
你想看见啥 Tony?
What do you expect to see,Tony?

471
00:24:33,810 --> 00:24:36,240
你不用追踪手机了 她在家
You don't have to track her cell.She's home.

472
00:24:37,090 --> 00:24:39,020
她在做什么?
What's she doing?

473
00:24:39,140 --> 00:24:40,690
没做什么
Not much.

474
00:24:40,770 --> 00:24:42,960
我们最好通知Gibbs
We better call Gibbs.

475
00:24:52,890 --> 00:24:54,310
她是平民
She's a civilian.

476
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,270
我要要回尸体
I want the body.

477
00:24:55,330 --> 00:24:56,930
不行 是我们找到的
No.We found her.

478
00:24:57,030 --> 00:24:59,800
她是找到杀手的主要线索
She's our lead to who may have put out the hit out on the commander.

479
00:24:59,900 --> 00:25:01,990
她现在死了 对你们也没啥帮助了
A lot of good she's going to do you dead.

480
00:25:02,070 --> 00:25:03,810
留下什么自杀遗言没有?
She leave a suicide note?

481
00:25:03,930 --> 00:25:06,530
刚刚去世的Turner小姐不是自杀的
The late Ms.Turner did not commit suicide.

482
00:25:06,610 --> 00:25:07,750
你说啥呢?
What are you talking about?

483
00:25:07,820 --> 00:25:09,060
她自己上吊的
She hung herself.

484
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:11,830
Mallard医生 这是警探Sportelli
Dr. Mallard,meet Metro Detective Sportelli.

485
00:25:11,860 --> 00:25:15,580
- 早 我应该跟您握手 但是... - 啊 没关系
- Good morning I'd shake hands,but,uh... - Ah,I'm cool.

486
00:25:15,580 --> 00:25:16,570
你怎么想 Duck?
What are you thinking,Duck?

487
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:18,110
上吊是掩饰
Well,the hanging was staged.

488
00:25:18,180 --> 00:25:19,090
你怎么知道?
How can you tell?

489
00:25:19,180 --> 00:25:25,040
这么说吧 上吊自杀是很少为女性所采用的 非常不典型
Well,to begin with,suicide by hanging is very unusual,uncharacteristic for a female.

490
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:26,870
所以我对此很怀疑
So I was suspicious.

491
00:25:26,940 --> 00:25:29,480
人体组织在死后的表现是不一样的
Human flesh reacts differently after death.

492
00:25:29,540 --> 00:25:34,890
当一个人上吊自杀 因为体重的关系 他的脖子会被往上吊起
When a person hangs themself,they are suspended by the neck with the weight of the body pulling downwards.

493
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:39,890
吊绳会在皮肤上形成前后深浅不一的痕迹
