00:34:28,720 --> 00:34:30,620
Brett没法解释他的大宗收入
Brett couldn't explain his massive income.

651
00:34:30,690 --> 00:34:32,570
并非来自他的军队补助
Not on a Navy salary.

652
00:34:32,690 --> 00:34:37,030
他需要把钱洗干净 所以他需要来自 他的甜心加会计Drew Turner的帮忙
He had to launder it,so he got a little help from his bar honey/accountant,Drew Turner.

653
00:34:37,110 --> 00:34:38,890
他们创造了虚拟的George Kaplan
They created the fictitious George Kaplan,

654
00:34:38,970 --> 00:34:42,460
接着通过经济账号 把钱漂白
then they ran the money through the brokerage account,so they could make it legal.

655
00:34:42,730 --> 00:34:44,210
这法子真行
It was brilliant.

656
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:47,750
是啊 直到出了岔子
Yeah. Until it went sideways.

657
00:35:13,850 --> 00:35:15,220
很可爱 对不对?
Cute,huh?

658
00:35:15,410 --> 00:35:17,790
他脾气可好了
He has a great personality.

659
00:35:18,070 --> 00:35:19,270
你想不想抱他?
You want to hold him?

660
00:35:28,120 --> 00:35:30,500
我是不是认识你?
Do I know you from somewhere?

661
00:35:30,630 --> 00:35:32,730
我不觉得
Um,I don't think so.

662
00:35:37,530 --> 00:35:39,880
11街的狗狗公园 对吗?
The dog park on 11th,right?

663
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:42,030
我从没去过那儿
I've never been there.

664
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:44,820
你看上去真挺眼熟的
You sure look familiar.

665
00:35:47,070 --> 00:35:49,490
你有想过今天带一只狗狗回家吗?
Are you looking to rescue a pet today?

666
00:35:49,860 --> 00:35:51,210
呃...没这个打算
Um... no.

667
00:35:51,560 --> 00:35:53,800
我是--随便逛逛
I wa-- I was just window-shopping.

668
00:35:53,910 --> 00:35:57,370
不过 我-我很欣赏你在这里做的一切
But I-I really admire what you do here.

669
00:35:58,090 --> 00:36:00,070
我喜欢你的狗颈圈
I love your dog collar.

670
00:36:00,190 --> 00:36:02,850
我们这儿有只斗牛犬也有个一样的
We have a pit bull terrier that has one just like it.

671
00:36:03,510 --> 00:36:06,300
来-进来看看 我... 你会喜欢上它的
Come-come take a look.I'm... You'll get a kick out of her.

672
00:36:08,450 --> 00:36:10,110
来吧
Come on.

673
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:15,330
过几天就要投票了
The vote's in a couple days.

674
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:18,320
跟被拽回NCIS相比 我有更好的事做
I have better things to do than be dragged back to NCIS.

675
00:36:18,390 --> 00:36:20,030
我们在案子上有突破
We had a break in the case.

676
00:36:20,270 --> 00:36:22,850
你为啥不告诉我啥情况?
Why don't you just tell me what it is?

677
00:36:26,550 --> 00:36:28,680
"审问室"?
"Interrogation Room"?

678
00:36:28,790 --> 00:36:30,600
哦 听上去可不妙啊
Well,that doesn't sound good.

679
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:35,700
不好意思 不知道这间有人了
Sorry.Did not know this room was used.

680
00:36:35,830 --> 00:36:36,970
不是问题
Not a problem.

681
00:36:37,050 --> 00:36:38,770
马上要收尾了
Just finishing up here.

682
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:40,730
你认识Nick Sandlock
You know Nick Sandlock.

683
00:36:42,540 --> 00:36:46,780
我们刚才在聊Stembridge 回扣啊 瑞士银行啥的
We were just talking about Stembridge,kickbacks and Swiss banks.

684
00:36:49,170 --> 00:36:51,400
我们能在这边聊
We can talk in here.

685
00:36:53,010 --> 00:36:54,590
拜拜
Bye-bye.

686
00:37:00,970 --> 00:37:03,650
我是特别探员McGee
Special Agent McGee.

687
00:37:05,650 --> 00:37:07,980
你看上需要坐下歇会儿 司令官
You look like you may need to sit down,Commander.

688
00:37:08,120 --> 00:37:12,420
是啊 直到Drew Turner惹了麻烦之前 都进展的不错
Yeah,sounded like a pretty sweet plan till Drew Turner got in trouble.

689
00:37:12,570 --> 00:37:14,950
那是什么 哥斯达黎加?
What was it,Costa Rica?

690
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:17,060
她赌博?
Her gambling?

691
00:37:18,820 --> 00:37:20,870
她赌博成瘾
She was addicted to it.

692
00:37:20,940 --> 00:37:24,380
你何时意识到她在用你的钱还赌债?
When did you realize she was using your money to pay off her bets?

693
00:37:25,230 --> 00:37:28,300
当你说"George Kaplan"要暗杀我的时候
When you said "George Kaplan" took out a hit on me.

694
00:37:29,700 --> 00:37:31,760
只有Drew知道这个名字
Drew was the only other person who knew that name.

695
00:37:31,810 --> 00:37:34,720
你要是死了 她就能动账户里的所有钱
With you dead,she'd have access to everything in the account.

696
00:37:37,410 --> 00:37:39,820
那个贪财的婊子为了钱杀我
The greedy bitch used the money to have me killed.

697
00:37:39,890 --> 00:37:42,510
这就是你为啥甩了Ziva? 嗯?
That why you ditched Ziva?Hmm?

698
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:45,540
所以你可以去干掉她?
So you could go after her?

699
00:37:46,370 --> 00:37:49,490
我是为了我女儿存的钱
I was putting that money away for my daughter.

700
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:53,430
为了她将来
For her future needs.

701
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:08,050
我认为现在我需要一个律师
I think this is where I tell you I need to talk to a lawyer.

702
00:38:28,830 --> 00:38:31,700
<i>坚忍号
***

703
00:38:35,600 --> 00:38:37,360
门没锁 Abbs
Door's unlocked,Abbs.

704
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:38,900
嗨 Gibbs.
Hi,Gibbs.

705
00:38:43,860 --> 00:38:46,220
怎么样? 你见过那人了?
So? You see the guy?

706
00:38:46,300 --> 00:38:50,110
Kyle? 我兄弟?没错
Kyle?My brother? - Yeah.

707
00:38:53,110 --> 00:38:54,670
怎么样?
How'd it go?

708
00:38:54,770 --> 00:38:58,450
挺好的 我没跟他说我是谁
It was fine. I didn't tell him who I was.

709
00:38:58,490 --> 00:39:01,370
他看上去真的是个好人
He seems really,really nice.

710
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:02,620
他不需要其他的压力了
He doesn't need the added stress.

711
00:39:02,720 --> 00:39:06,130
我是说 他刚被选上去捐肾 手术明天进行
I mean,he just got chosen to donate a kidney,and the operation's tomorrow.

712
00:39:06,230 --> 00:39:09,850
我只是...需要理清一些头绪 你知道?
I just... I have things I have to work out,you know?

713
00:39:09,970 --> 00:39:12,040
你在喝茶吗?
Are you drinking tea?

714
00:39:12,310 --> 00:39:16,950
对啊 别告诉Ducky 他非得给我上一课
Yeah.Don't tell Ducky.He'll give me a lecture on brewing.

715
00:39:17,950 --> 00:39:19,910
你需要想清楚什么 Abbs?
What do you need to work out,Abbs?

716
00:39:20,510 --> 00:39:25,680
就是...这个兄妹事呗
Just... this whole brother-sister thing.

717
00:39:25,980 --> 00:39:28,160
我对此毫无头绪
It didn't make any sense to me.

718
00:39:28,260 --> 00:39:32,680
我是说 Kyle和我--我们的DNA完全吻合
I mean,Kyle and me-- our DNA is a total match.

719
00:39:32,820 --> 00:39:35,630
也就是说我们拥有共同的生父母
So,we have to have the same biological parents.

720
00:39:35,740 --> 00:39:40,500
所以我怎么说"嘿 为什么他们不要你?
So then I was like,"What,did they give him up for adoption?

721
00:39:40,730 --> 00:39:49,050
而我很难想象一对养育大我和Luca的完美父母竟然会放弃另一个孩子
And I-I can't imagine the wonderful,loving parents that raised me and Luca ever giving up a child.

722
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:53,620
可他们可以收养一个孩子
But they would have adopted a child.

723
00:39:53,740 --> 00:39:56,340
他们这么做了
And they did.

724
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:58,880
就是我
Me.

725
00:40:02,380 --> 00:40:04,680
我是被收养的 Gibbs
I'm adopted,Gibbs.

726
00:40:05,170 --> 00:40:07,350
你是怎么发现的?
How do you know that?

727
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:14,250
这是我妈妈的头发
This is my mom's hair.

728
00:40:14,360 --> 00:40:19,510
我对它做了DNA测试 和我的进行了对比
And I ran a DNA test on it and I compared it to mine.

729
00:40:20,700 --> 00:40:23,180
它们在生物学上不吻合 Gibbs
It wasn't a biological match,Gibbs.

730
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:29,360
所以 我...我都知道自己是谁了
So I... I don't know who I am anymore.

731
00:40:29,470 --> 00:40:32,750
我甚至连自己的父母都不知道
I don't know who my parents were.

732
00:40:32,830 --> 00:40:37,200
我就像个...像个小孤儿Abby
I'm just like... like Little Orphan Abby.

733
00:40:37,300 --> 00:40:40,840
Abbs...你还是你
Abbs... you're still the same person.

734
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:47,380
你的父母--还是你的父母 只要你记得他们
Your parents-- they're still your parents,as you remember them.

735
00:40:50,830 --> 00:40:54,870
亲人可远不是...DNA
Family's more than just... DNA.

736
00:40:57,730 --> 00:41:03,800
是...关心爱护你的人们
It's about.. people who care and take care of each other.

737
00:41:03,910 --> 00:41:05,590
我知道
I know.

738
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:11,810
可他们为什么不告诉我是领养的?
But why didn't they tell me I was adopted?

739
00:41:12,020 --> 00:41:13,970
我是说 总有个原因
I mean,there's got to be a reason.

740
00:41:14,060 --> 00:41:21,930
我是说我得查出来 在我把Luca和Kyle 的生活弄得天翻地覆之前
And I need to find out before I completely turn Luca and Kyle's lives upside down.

741
00:41:24,390 --> 00:41:27,260
你没必要自己一个人去做 Abby
You don't have to do this alone,Abby.

742
00:41:29,340 --> 00:41:32,530
你有家人
You've got a family.

743
00:41:32,720 --> 00:41:35,300
我们也会帮你度过难关
And we'll help you through it.


